version_description: Phone Tracker has added following features. Locate Phone, Send Sound to Phone, Low Battery GPS Send and Lost Phone Message functions. Enhancements were also made to navigation to improve user interface.

Phone Tracker has added the following new features - Panic Button and a Free U.S. Area Code Search. Enhancements were also made to the
screen and to navigation to improve user interface.

New Streamlined User Interface. Added A View Phone Contacts feature. App will make copy of First Names, Last Names and Phone Numbers from Child's Phone Contact List. You will then be able to see who your family have been conversing with.
Updated terms, minor back end fixes, and added new screenshots
Added Support for additional languages. Streamlined Interface.
